implementationPlan.description:
B21 Fix: Add null checks to moe-agent.ps1 team setup. In scripts/moe-agent.ps1 (~line 538-549), before indexing into the MCP response, add validation:
```powershell
if ($createResult -and $createResult.result -and $createResult.result.content -and $createResult.result.content.Count -gt 0) {
    $teamObj = $createResult.result.content[0].text | ConvertFrom-Json
    ...
} else {
    Write-Host 'WARNING: Could not parse team creation response' -ForegroundColor Yellow
}
```
Also add the same null-safety to the join_team response parsing. Error handling: on parse failure, continue without team context (agent still works, just without team awareness).
